0.03  Thu Jul 25 15:27:43 CEST 2008 (Marcel Gruenauer <marcel@cpan.org>)
     - Changed dist style and Changes back to standard. People didn't like it -
       the nail that sticks out gets hammered down.
     - Added standard test files; this will also help with CPANTS.

0.02  Thu, 29 May 2008 12:01:28 -0000 (Marcel Gruenauer <marcel@cpan.org>)
     - Moved to YAML Changes file
     - Added auto_install feature 'Generated documentation' that requires
       Pod::Generated
     - .shipit: added Twitter step
     - Makefile.PL: added auto_install() and process_templates()
     - lib/*: converted to template
     - updated MANIFEST
     - add documentation on the 'purpose' and 'example' keys taken by
       install_accessor()
     - updated t/perlcriticrc
     - Changes: fixed global.name
     - .shipit: fixed svk.tagpattern
     - tags: NEWFEATURE

